{"title":"Thok TP4 Transforms 3D-Printed Light eBike into a Full-Power Carbon eMTB Shredder","link":"https://bikerumor.com/thok-tp4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-ebike-bosch-cx-emtb-made-in-italy/","date":1730916180000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike-1536x1024.webp\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"Thok TP4 modular carbon all-mountain eMTB with Bosch CX motor and variable batteries, made-in-Italy\" /></p>\n<p>Last summer’s 3D-printed aluminum Project 4 eMTB is reborn as the now-carbon Thok TP4, a full-power all-mountain ebike that retains modular batteries so you get only the juice you want and no extra weight. Thok’s first Bosch eMTB gets fitted with the latest CX motor update, and the option for anywhere from 400Wh-1050Wh batteries to suit each buyer’s style of riding.,</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Thok TP4 Italian carbon all-mountain ebike</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_riding-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_riding-jpg.webp\" alt=\"Thok TP4 modular carbon all-mountain eMTB with Bosch CX motor and variable batteries, made-in-Italy, riding\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_riding-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_riding-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_riding-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_riding-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_riding-768x461.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos/Thok)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Last year at Eurobike Thok teased us with <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/thok-project-4-emtb-is-worlds-first-3d-printed-alloy-full-suspension-ebike/\" target=\"_blank\">Project 4</a>, what they called the world’s first 3D-printed alloy full-suspension ebike. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Thok-Project-4-eMTB-prototype_lightweight-3D-printed-alloy-all-mountain-ebike.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Thok-Project-4-eMTB-prototype_lightweight-3D-printed-alloy-all-mountain-ebike.jpg\" alt=\"Thok Project 4 eMTB prototype, lightweight 3D-printed alloy all-mountain ebike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Thok-Project-4-eMTB-prototype_lightweight-3D-printed-alloy-all-mountain-ebike.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Thok-Project-4-eMTB-prototype_lightweight-3D-printed-alloy-all-mountain-ebike-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Thok-Project-4-eMTB-prototype_lightweight-3D-printed-alloy-all-mountain-ebike-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Thok-Project-4-eMTB-prototype_lightweight-3D-printed-alloy-all-mountain-ebike-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Thok-Project-4-eMTB-prototype_lightweight-3D-printed-alloy-all-mountain-ebike-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Thok-Project-4-eMTB-prototype_lightweight-3D-printed-alloy-all-mountain-ebike-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Thok-Project-4-eMTB-prototype_lightweight-3D-printed-alloy-all-mountain-ebike-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photo/Cory Benson)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, it turns out that modular eMTB project was simply the rapidly-developed test bed for Thok’s first ebike with a Bosch CX motor. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>And what was made quickly with additive manufacturing in aluminum to dial in the shaping and geometry, is now being made entirely in Italy out of carbon fiber.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-all-mountain-eMTB_carbon-ebike-frame-made-in-Italy-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"1200\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-all-mountain-eMTB_carbon-ebike-frame-made-in-Italy-jpg.webp\" alt=\"Thok TP4 modular carbon all-mountain eMTB with Bosch CX motor and variable batteries, carbon frameset made-in-Italy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-all-mountain-eMTB_carbon-ebike-frame-made-in-Italy-jpg.webp 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-all-mountain-eMTB_carbon-ebike-frame-made-in-Italy-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-all-mountain-eMTB_carbon-ebike-frame-made-in-Italy-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-all-mountain-eMTB_carbon-ebike-frame-made-in-Italy-768x461.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Thok TP4 is mid-travel 29er eMTB with 150mm of 4-bar rear wheel travel mated to 160mm up front. Thok calls it “<em>enhanced all-mountain with an enduro side to it</em>“. While building an all-new made-in-Italy eMTB platform around the new lighter, smoother, and quieter <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/boschs-new-performance-cx-ebike-motor-is-not-more-powerful-but-is-better-and-lighter/\" target=\"_blank\">Bosch Performance Line CX</a> motor, Thok wanted to create a technically-capable do-it-all-mountain ebike that riders could tailor to their needs with the precise battery size that they needed. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Modular battery size was a key point of the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/thok-project-4-emtb-is-worlds-first-3d-printed-alloy-full-suspension-ebike/\" target=\"_blank\">original 3D-printed project bike</a>. And they carry that on here with an adaptable battery cradle inside the downtube that can secure 3 sizes of batteries behind the removable battery cover/downtube protector.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Slacker geometry for all-mountain eMTB versatility</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_non-driveside-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2500\" height=\"1400\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_non-driveside-jpg.webp\" alt=\"Thok TP4 modular carbon all-mountain eMTB with Bosch CX motor and variable batteries, non-driveside\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_non-driveside-jpg.webp 2500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_non-driveside-297x166.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_non-driveside-1536x860.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_non-driveside-120x67.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_non-driveside-768x430.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_non-driveside-2048x1147.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Compared to Thok’s shorter travel all-mountain MIG (140/150mm) and longer-travel e-enduro TK01 (170/170mm ), the new TP4 is actually as slack or slacker than either. Thok says that was about bridging the gap between the two, while creating and even more versatile all-mountain ebike capable of riding any terrain.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_adjustable-geometry-scaled.webp\"><img width=\"2560\" height=\"768\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_adjustable-geometry-scaled.webp\" alt=\"Thok TP4 modular carbon all-mountain eMTB with Bosch CX motor and variable batteries, adjustable geometry\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_adjustable-geometry-scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_adjustable-geometry-297x89.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_adjustable-geometry-1536x461.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_adjustable-geometry-120x36.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_adjustable-geometry-768x230.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_adjustable-geometry-2048x614.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Start off with a 64.5° headtube angle, 79° seattube, 459mm chainstays, and 477mm size L Reach.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And thanks to the Hi/Lo flip-chip at the forward shock mount, riders can further slacken the geometry by 0.5° (and lower BB height 9mm). Or even run it in the Hi position with a 27.5″ rear wheel for a slacker mullet conversion.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Tech details</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>hi-mod carbon frame with alloy rocker, made-in-Italy</li>\n\n\n\n<li>3.5kg bare carbon frame weight (size M, <em>claimed</em>)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>full 29er setup with 150mm travel rear pair to 160mm forks</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_new-Bosch-Performance-Line-CX-motor-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_new-Bosch-Performance-Line-CX-motor-jpg.webp\" alt=\"Thok TP4 modular carbon all-mountain eMTB with Bosch Performance Line CX motor\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_new-Bosch-Performance-Line-CX-motor-jpg.webp 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_new-Bosch-Performance-Line-CX-motor-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_new-Bosch-Performance-Line-CX-motor-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_new-Bosch-Performance-Line-CX-motor-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_new-Bosch-Performance-Line-CX-motor-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_new-Bosch-Performance-Line-CX-motor-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_new-Bosch-Performance-Line-CX-motor-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>powered by the latest 85Nm Bosch Performance Line CX motor (<a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/boschs-new-performance-cx-ebike-motor-is-not-more-powerful-but-is-better-and-lighter/\" target=\"_blank\">BDU384Y</a>)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>grip-mounted Purion 200 display</li>\n\n\n\n<li>choice of 400Wh, 600Wh, or 800Wh internal batteries</li>\n\n\n\n<li>plus optional 250Wh PowerMore range extender external battery</li>\n\n\n\n<li>tapered 1.5″ headset</li>\n\n\n\n<li>internal cables routed through the outside of the headtube</li>\n\n\n\n<li>forward shock mount flip-chip for adaptable geometry or also mullet conversions</li>\n\n\n\n<li>UDH compatibility with mechanical or electronic drivetrains</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_UDH-detail-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"900\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_UDH-detail-jpg.webp\" alt=\"Thok TP4 modular carbon all-mountain eMTB with Bosch CX motor and variable batteries, made-in-Italy, UDH\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_UDH-detail-jpg.webp 900w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_UDH-detail-225x300.webp 225w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_UDH-detail-90x120.webp 90w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_UDH-detail-768x1024.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_flip-chip-detail-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"900\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_flip-chip-detail-jpg.webp\" alt=\"Thok TP4 modular carbon all-mountain eMTB with Bosch CX motor and variable batteries, made-in-Italy, flip-chip\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_flip-chip-detail-jpg.webp 900w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_flip-chip-detail-225x300.webp 225w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_flip-chip-detail-90x120.webp 90w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_flip-chip-detail-768x1024.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_headtube-detail-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"900\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_headtube-detail-jpg.webp\" alt=\"Thok TP4 modular carbon all-mountain eMTB with Bosch CX motor and variable batteries, made-in-Italy, headtube\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_headtube-detail-jpg.webp 900w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_headtube-detail-225x300.webp 225w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_headtube-detail-90x120.webp 90w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_headtube-detail-768x1024.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Thok TP4 ebikes – Pricing, options &amp; availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_NDS-angled-rear-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_NDS-angled-rear-jpg.webp\" alt=\"Thok TP4 modular carbon all-mountain eMTB with Bosch CX motor and variable batteries, angled rear\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_NDS-angled-rear-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_NDS-angled-rear-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_NDS-angled-rear-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_NDS-angled-rear-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_NDS-angled-rear-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_NDS-angled-rear-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_NDS-angled-rear-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new carbon Thok TP4 eMTB comes in 2 complete ebike builds – both of which come standard with the big 800Wh battery. But all buyers can opt for a smaller battery if they want, to save both money and weight.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The TP4-R is the ‘more affordable’ option at 7190€ with Fox 36 &amp; Float X Performance suspension, a mechanical XT drivetrain, 4-piston Magura MT5, and then alloy DT H1900 wheels wrapped in the great new Schwalbe Albert Gravity Radial tires – at a claimed 24.3kg complete (size M).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_TP4-R-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2500\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_TP4-R-jpg.webp\" alt=\"Thok TP4 modular carbon all-mountain eMTB with Bosch CX motor and variable batteries, made-in-Italy, R\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_TP4-R-jpg.webp 2500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_TP4-R-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_TP4-R-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_TP4-R-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_TP4-R-768x461.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_TP4-R-2048x1229.webp 2048w\" /></a><figcaption>Thok TP4-R</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The much more expensive 10,490€ TP4-LTD steps it up to Öhlins RXF36 fork, TTX2 Air shock, SRAM GX Eagle electronic T-type derailleur wired into the ebike’s battery, Magura MT7 brakes, and carbon DT Swiss HXC1501 wheels with those Schwalbe Albert Gravity Radial tires – at a claimed 24.1kg. The LTD is also actually a limited edition, and Thok only make 30 of them.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_TP4-LTD-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2500\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_TP4-LTD-jpg.webp\" alt=\"Thok TP4 modular carbon all-mountain eMTB with Bosch CX motor and variable batteries, made-in-Italy, LTD\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_TP4-LTD-jpg.webp 2500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_TP4-LTD-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_TP4-LTD-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_TP4-LTD-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_TP4-LTD-768x461.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_TP4-LTD-2048x1229.webp 2048w\" /></a><figcaption>Thok TP4-LTD</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And if you prefer a smaller battery for either model, you can pick the smaller 600Wh option to then save 1.1kg &amp; 200€, or get the lightest 400Wh battery to save 2.2kg &amp; 400€ vs. the standard big battery setups. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_mountains-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_mountains-jpg.webp\" alt=\"Thok TP4 modular carbon all-mountain eMTB with Bosch CX motor and variable batteries, made-in-Italy, riding\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_mountains-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_mountains-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_mountains-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_mountains-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_mountains-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Thok-TP4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-eMTB_made-in-Italy_150mm-Bosch-CX-ebike_mountains-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Both versions are technically available to buy now. But Thok sold out the first small batch, so the next delivery comes next month in December.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.thokbikes.com/en/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>ThokBikes.com</em></a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/thok-tp4-modular-carbon-all-mountain-ebike-bosch-cx-emtb-made-in-italy/\">Thok TP4 Transforms 3D-Printed Light eBike into a Full-Power Carbon eMTB Shredder</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"f964d26c930f9ab2f9ab9bf31f0ab50bdd35732ea1df3fc792c22a109703abc5","category":"Cycling"}